<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١ - إِذْ قالَتِ امْرَأَتُ عِمْرانَ <span class="c4">[آل عمران: ٣٥]</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٢ - امْرَأَتُ الْعَزِيزِ تُراوِدُ <span class="c4">[يوسف: ٣٠]</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٣ - <span class="c2">(قالت امرأت العزيز)</span> <span class="c4">[يوسف: ٥١]</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٤ - وَقالَتِ امْرَأَتُ فِرْعَوْنَ <span class="c4">[القصص: ٩]</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٥ - امْرَأَتَ نُوحٍ <span class="c4">[التحريم: ١٠]</span>.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٦ - وَامْرَأَتَ لُوطٍ <span class="c4">[التحريم: ١٠]</span>.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٧ - امْرَأَتَ فِرْعَوْنَ <span class="c4">[التحريم: ١١]</span>.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>